<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to XroboFly</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .header {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35 0%, #F7931E 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #111827;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }
        .welcome-message {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .welcome-message h2 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .welcome-message p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .user-info {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .user-info h3 {
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #374151;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
        }
        .info-value {
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        .features {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .features h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .feature-list {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .feature-item {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 3px solid #111827;
        }
        .feature-item strong {
            color: #111827;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .feature-item span {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .cta-button a {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #111827;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta-button a:hover {
            background: #1f2937;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .footer p {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .footer .social-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .footer .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #111827;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .security-note {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .security-note p {
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üöÅ</div>
            <h1>XroboFly</h1>
            <p>Your Premium E-Commerce Platform</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome-message">
                <h2>Welcome Aboard, {{name}}! üéâ</h2>
                <p>Thank you for joining XroboFly! We're thrilled to have you as part of our community.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="user-info">
                <h3>üìã Account Details</h3>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Name:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{name}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Email:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{email}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Account Created:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{registrationDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Account Role:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{role}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="features">
                <h3>‚ú® What's Waiting for You</h3>
                <div class="feature-list">
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <strong>üõçÔ∏è Shop</strong>
                        <span>Browse premium products</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <strong>üõí Cart</strong>
                        <span>Easy checkout process</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <strong>üì¶ Orders</strong>
                        <span>Track your purchases</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <strong>‚≠ê Reviews</strong>
                        <span>Share your feedback</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-button">
                <a href="{{frontendUrl}}">Start Shopping Now</a>
            </div>

            <div class="security-note">
                <p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Notice:</strong> We never ask for your password via email. If you didn't create this account, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© {{year}} XroboFly. All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Facebook</a>
                <a href="#">Twitter</a>
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
            </div>
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@ecom.com" style="color: #667eea;">support@ecom.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
